<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Untitled</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Untitled</CENTER></H2>

Night Fallen<BR>
bass guitar at my side<BR>
you are sleeping<BR>
and you smile<BR>
movement outside in the dark<BR>
dogs in the yard<BR>
and rain<BR>
cleaning<BR>
