<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) &amp; Open Government&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000EE" VLINK="03066A" ALINK="FF0000">

