<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/earth3_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Global Internet Censorship&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Global/Dispatches/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Fri Aug 16 13:18:50 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<br>
   Maintained by Declan McCullagh, declan@eff.org
<p>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
