<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_trans_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF "Legal Cases - FOIA/Privacy - EPIC v. FBI (Digital Telephony & Clipper)" Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org /pub/Privacy/Surveillance/EPIC_v_FBI/
<br>gopher.eff.org 1/Privacy/Surveillance/EPIC_v_FBI
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Surveillance/EPIC_v_FBI/
</H5>



<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#onsite">On-Site Links</A></TD><H1></H1>
<TD><A HREF="#offsite">Off-Site Links</A></TD>
