<a name="top">EFF &quot;Legal Cases&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Legal/Cases/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Nov 06 14:24:30 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
