<a name="top">EFF "Legal Cases - FOIA/Privacy - CPSR v. FBI (Digital Telephony)" Archive</a></h1>

<H5>ftp.eff.org, /pub/Privacy/Surveillance/CPSR_v_FBI/
<br>gopher.eff.org, 1/Privacy/Surveillance/CPSR_v_FBI
<br>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Surveillance/CPSR_v_FBI/
</H5>



<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
