<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Green Tree</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Green Tree</CENTER></H2>
Green, green tree<BR>
burn bright your arms<BR>
look to the south<BR>
eyes which lie I don't know<BR>
where shall we sleep<BR>
to see the ocean black<BR>
in the depths of her mind<BR>
green, green tree<BR>
take me away to another time<BR>
the slow dance of grass<BR>
weeds of our love<BR>
<P>footsteps echoing through the courtyard<P>
green, green tree<BR>
diagonal tiles into infinity<BR>
do you see me in your hour of light<BR>
burn brighter to freeze<BR>
freeze in time.<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
