<H2><A NAME="dirs">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/filefolder_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40
ALT=""></A> Subdirectories in This Archive</H2>

<DL>
<DT><A HREF=".."><B>Up to the Parent Directory</B><P></a>
<DT><a href="Legal/"><B>Legal/</B></A>
<DD>A full copy of all the legal documents in the case (except some
    that the government submitted but would not provide in machine-readable
    form, and a few that were copies of published material).
<DT><a href="Letters/"><B>Letters/</B></A>
<DD>Directory containing the original letters between Bernstein 
    and various officials regarding the export of the Snuffle 
    encryption algorithm and program. Some of these items are 
    also exhibits in the case.
</DL>

