<b>Comments:</B><BLOCKQUOTE>    
 I enjoyed your essay.  I agree that we each have the power to affect or neglect our world. While it is important to be aware of the injustices of the world, it is also important not to simply dwell on the horror of it all.  The human spirit, which we acess through our own creativity, brings harmony into the world.  Along with the facts we need humor, aesthetics, and expression.  I'm not saying a spoonful of sugar will help the medicine go down; I'm saying we need something more to lift our spirits and to reaffirm the life force, which is creative by nature.   </BLOCKQUOTE><HR>

