<P></CENTER><BR><HR>
<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="arc602.tos"><B>arc602.tos</B></a>
<DD>self-extracting archive with Arc version 6.02 and a shell
    with a graphical user-interface; for making and extracting
    ARC compressed archives on the Atari (mostly for FidoNet mail).
<DT><a href="stzip24.tos"><B>stzip24.tos</B></a>
<DD>self-extracting archive with STZip version 2.4 (corresponding
    to version 2.0? on other machines). This archive doesn't
    create a folder when it extracts; it needs 290 kB free disk
    space. For creating and extracting ZIP format compressed
    archives on the Atari.
<DT><a href="zooatari.tos"><B>zooatari.tos</B></a>
<DD>ZOO 2.1 for Atari ST; self-extracting archive. For creating
    and extracting ZOO format compressed archives (mostly found
    on DOS and Unix systems).
</DL>

