<h2><A NAME="onsite">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/door_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 
ALT=""></A> Related On-Site Resources</h2>
<DL>

<DT><B>EFF <A HREF="/pub/Privacy/">Privacy, Cryptography &amp; Security</A>
Archive</B>
<DT><a href="/pub/Privacy/ITAR_export/Junger_v_DoS/"><B>Peter Junger's lawsuit</B></A>
<DD>Professor Junger's lawsuit over whether the First
    Amendment gives him the right to teach a class in which cryptography
    is detailed, if a foreign student is present.
<DT><a href="/pub/Privacy/ITAR_export/Karn_Schneier_export_case/"><B>Phil Karn's lawsuit</B></A>
<DD>Phil Karn's lawsuit over whether he can export some source code from
Bruce Schneier's book &quot;Applied Cryptography&quot;.


</DL>

