<DT><a href="950922_tien.exhibits/"><B>950922_tien.exhibits/</B></A>
<DD>The Justice Department memos themselves.
<DT><a href="950221.exhibits/"><B>950221.exhibits/</B></A>
<DD>The exhibit documents filed with the original
    complaint.
</DL>

