<DOCNO>WT10-B06-167</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000559-B021-69</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/pub/Net_info/Guidebooks/Hytelnet/Unix/ 204.253.162.4 19970103130651 text/html 5695
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 13:06:50 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
