<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/door_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 
ALT=""></A> Related On-Site Resources</h2>
<DL>

<DT><B><A HREF="/papers/eegtti/eegttitop.html">Browse the HTML (WWW) 
Hypertext Edition of <I>EFF's (Extended) Guide to the Internet</I></B>
</DL>

