<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Privacy &amp; Free Speech - G7 Anti-Internet Resolutions&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Key_escrow/G7/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Thu Aug 08 10:35:43 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
