    Disinfected for Your Protection&quot;; article by Declan McCullagh on G7 
    resolutions to restrict the Internet, and US Atty. Gen. Reno's 
    announcement of G7 support for encryption key &quot;escrow&quot;. (July 31, 1996)
</DL>

