<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Simple Song</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Simple Song</CENTER></H2>
Here is a simple song<BR>
heartfelt though not long<BR>
meant to clarify <BR>
the words that I<BR>
have muttered in such varried verses understandable only to me<BR>
that is, to make clear how dearly I love thee.<BR>
<P>
And here is the other verse<BR>
to fill in the gaps in the first<BR>
which is only a thanks from me<BR>
for being the ground under my feet<BR>
and both the structure and the tucker-under-the-covers and sheets<BR>
of my reality<BR>
from which I stray<BR>
into the sea of illusion which is my life.<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
