<DD>Illinois Freedom of Information Act of July 1983 declaring
    it to be the public policy of the State of Illinois that all persons
    are entitled to full and complete information regarding the affairs of
    government and the official acts and policies of those who represent
    them as public officials and public employees consistent with the
    terms of the Act
