<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Cool Shades</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Cool Shades</H2></CENTER>

White, white<BR>
penetrating, bright<BR>
shading my eyes against the light<BR>
not shiny<BR>
not pretty<BR>
not on my knees adoringly<BR>
harsh and blindingly<BR>
beyond the greens and blues<BR>
and other people's moods<BR>
another brilliant fool<BR>
who'd have the answer if you'd just give him<BR>
some cool shades.<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
