<BR><h2><A NAME="files">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/doc1_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 ALT=""></A>
Files in this Archive</h2>

<DL>
<DT><a href="bsa_escrow_090695.testimony"><B>bsa_escrow_090695.testimony</B></a>
<DD>Business Software Alliance testimony at
    NIST Sept 6 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="cdt_escrow_090795.testimony"><B>cdt_escrow_090795.testimony</B></a>
<DD>Center for Democracy &amp; Technology testimony
    at NIST Sept 7 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="denning_escrow_090695.testimony"><B>denning_escrow_090695.testimony</B></a>
<DD>Prof. Dorothy Denning testimony at NIST
    Sept 6 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="ellison_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary"><B>ellison_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary</B></a>
<DD>Carl Ellison's summary of the
    Sept 6-7 95 NIST key escrow meetings.
<DT><a href="farrell_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary"><B>farrell_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary</B></a>
<DD>Pat Farrell's summary of the
    Sept 6-7 95 NIST key escrow meetings.
<DT><a href="hoffman_ictsp_escrow_090795.presentation"><B>hoffman_ictsp_escrow_090795.presentation</B></a>
<DD>Lance Hoffman of ICTSP
    presentation at NIST Sept 7 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="lesher_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary"><B>lesher_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary</B></a>
<DD>David Lesher's summary of the
    Sept 6-7 95 NIST key escrow meetings.
<DT><a href="lewis_960911_escrow.article"><B>lewis_960911_escrow.article</B></a>
<DD>Peter Lewis column on &quot;Clipper II&quot; key escrow
    and Clinton Administration crypto export policy. Good backgrounder if
    you're new to the issue.
<DT><a href="nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.agendas"><B>nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.agendas</B></a>
<DD>4 &quot;workshop&quot; agendas for the NIST
    Sept. 6-7 key escrow meetings. (see below for original press release.)
    The last of the 4 is essentially a new Clinton Administration
    cryptography export policy.
<DT><a href="nist_key_escrow_meet_95_announce.old"><B>nist_key_escrow_meet_95_announce.old</B></a>
<DD>Original NIST announcement
    of semi-public NIST meetings on commercial key escrow (labelled
    &quot;Clipper 2&quot; by privacy advocates). The meetings were held Sept. 6-7 1995.
<DT><a href="nist_wh_escrow_090695_testimony.outline"><B>nist_wh_escrow_090695_testimony.outline</B></a>
<DD>NIST and White House testimony
    at NIST Sept 6 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="plesser_nist_key_escrow.analysis"><B>plesser_nist_key_escrow.analysis</B></a>
<DD>Ron Plesser (Piper &amp; Marbury, CIX)
    analysis of new NIST key escrow &amp; export policy drafts, and the Sept. 95
    meetings.
<DT><a href="sweet_ns_escrow_090695.testimony"><B>sweet_ns_escrow_090695.testimony</B></a>
<DD>Bill Sweet (National Semiconductor)
    testimony at NIST Sept 6 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="tecsec_escrow_090695.testimony"><B>tecsec_escrow_090695.testimony</B></a>
<DD>TECSEC testimony at NIST Sept 6 95 key
    escrow meeting
<DT><a href="tis_escrow_090695.testimony"><B>tis_escrow_090695.testimony</B></a>
<DD>Trusted Information Systems' testimony at
    NIST Sept 6 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="tis_escrow_090795.presentation"><B>tis_escrow_090795.presentation</B></a>
<DD>Trusted Info. Systems presentation at
    NIST Sept. 7 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="vtw_escrow_090695.testimony"><B>vtw_escrow_090695.testimony</B></a>
<DD>Voters Telecommunications Watch testimony
    at NIST Sept 6 95 key escrow meeting
<DT><a href="vtw_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary"><B>vtw_nist_key_escrow_meet_0995.summary</B></a>
<DD>Voters Telecom Watch summary of
    the Sept. 6-7 and Sept. 15 key escrow meetings held by NIST. The outlook
    is rather bleak.
<DT><a href="workgroup_nist_key_escrow_meet_090695.reports"><B>workgroup_nist_key_escrow_meet_090695.reports</B></a>
<DD>two reports from the
    temporary working groups of the NIST Sept. 6-7 key escrow meetings.
</DL>

