<DT><a href="Clipper/"><B>Clipper/</B></A>
<DD>Link to directory of documents on the original NSA &quot;Clipper&quot;
    digital wiretap key &quot;escrow&quot; system (1993-4)
<DT><a href="Clipper_III/"><B>Clipper_III/</B></A>
<DD>Link to directory of documents on the 1996 IWGCP
    draft key &quot;escrow&quot; scheme, referred to commonly as &quot;Clipper III&quot;
<DT><a href="Euro-Clipper/"><B>Euro-Clipper/</B></A>
<DD>directory of info on key &quot;escrow&quot; and &quot;trusted third party&quot;
    schemes in Europe, labelled &quot;Euro-Clipper&quot; by many.
</DL>

