<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Four Choices</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<H2><CENTER>Four Choices</H2>

What do you do at a time like this<BR>
Tell her she's a fool<BR>
or lie through your teeth<BR>
perhaps evade<BR>
or say nothing at all<BR>
anywhichway you take a fall.<BR>
</BODY></HTML>
