<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Dancing Girl</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR = "FFFFFF" TEXT = "000000">
<H2><CENTER>Dancing Girl</CENTER></H2>
like
<BR>wet
<BR>satin black
<BR>whips on the line to dry
<BR>to the whim of a flustered sky
<BR>she moves
<P>
like
<BR>trail of smoke
<BR>slips to heaven off
<BR>the amber tip of jasmine
<BR>she moves
<P>
chameleon
<BR>in an all mirrored box
<BR>reflects her soul
<BR>endless and active
<BR>she moves me.
</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
