<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/~erict/Personal/Prose/stpp_listserv.html 204.253.162.4 19970108040649 text/html 3751
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 08 Jan 1997 04:06:53 GMT
