</DL>

<br><hr><br>
<h2><A NAME="offsite">
<IMG SRC="/pub/Graphics/Icons/earth2_icon.gif" WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=40 ALT=""></A>
Links to Related Off-Site Resources</h2>
<DL>

<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.house.gov/white/internet_caucus/netcauc.html">The
Congressional Internet Caucus</A></B>
<DD>A new group of US legislators trying to protect the Internet
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.epic.org/crypto/ban/fbi_dox/">Declassified
documents reveal that, despite promises of "voluntary" key escrow, FBI and
NSA both believe that Clipper-like systems "will only work" if made
mandatory</A>
<DD>(docs available via EPIC web site)
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.epic.org/crypto/">Electronic Privacy Info.
Center's Encryption Policy</A> pages</B>
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.cdt.org/crypto">CDT Crypto Issues
Page</A></B>
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.crypto.com">Encryption Policy Resource
Pages</A></B>
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.privacy.org/ipc">Internet Privacy
Coalition</A></B>
<DT><B><A HREF="http://www.zdnet.com/intweek/daily/960518y.html">ZDNet story
on "Clipper III"</A></B>
</DL>

<br><hr><br>
<a href="mailto:webmaster@eff.org">webmaster@eff.org</a>
