<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>EFF &quot;Censorship - Washington (state)&quot; Archive</TITLE><LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:webmaster@eff.org"></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="FF0000">

<CENTER>
