<DOCNO>WT10-B06-308</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000564-B030-163</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://kragar.eff.org:80/pub/Net_info/Guidebooks/Zen_and_Internet/ 204.253.162.4 19970103191218 text/html 5298
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
