<a name="top">EFF &quot;Privacy - Crypto - Key Escrow 1993-4 (US): Clipper/EES/Capstone/Tessera/Skipjack&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Clipper/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Sep 18 11:59:38 PDT 1996</h6><br>
