<DD>No Description
<DT><a href="eegtti.gif"><B>eegtti.gif</B></a>
<DD>&quot;EFF's (Extended) Guide to the Internet&quot; title bar/logo
    (by Joke)
<DT><a href="eegttilogo.gif"><B>eegttilogo.gif</B></a>
<DD>&quot;EFF's (Extended) Guide to the Internet&quot; lifesaver logo
    (by Joke)
</DL>

