<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eegtti_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top"> &quot;EFF's Guide to the Internet - Misc. Other Versions &amp; Translations&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Net_info/EFF_Net_Guide/Other_versions/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Fri Sep 13 14:18:31 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<br>
   (formerly The Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet, published in hardcopy by
   MIT Press as Everybody's Guide to the Internet.)
<p>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="#files">Files</A></TD><h6></h6>
<TD><A HREF="#dirs">Subdirectories</A></TD><h6></h6>
<TD><A HREF="#onsite">On-Site Links</A></TD><h6></h6>
