<h1><img src="/pub/Graphics/Icons/eff3d_white_icon.gif" ALT="">
<a name="top">EFF &quot;Privacy - Crypto - Key Escrow &amp; Govt. Access to Keys&quot; Archive</a></h1>

<H5>http://www.eff.org/pub/Privacy/Key_escrow/
</H5>



<h6>Last Updated Wed Sep 18 11:58:58 PDT 1996</h6><br>
<TABLE BORDER=4 CELLPADDING=4 CELLSPACING=4>
